title: Carpride All Seasons Screen Wash, 1L Concentrated Formula
features: BRIGHT, STREAK-FREE WINDSCREEN: Carpride All Seasons Screenwash, a concentrated windscreen washer additive. It quickly removes dirt, grime & insect deposits from windscreens, leaving a bright streak-free finish.
ALL YEAR ROUND SCREEN WASH: Carpride All Seasons Screenwash, use throughout Spring, Summer, Autumn & Winter to maintain a clean, sparkling windscreen

EASY TO USE CONCENTRATED FORMULA: Carpride recommend diluting Normal Driving Conditons: 1 part screen wash to 4 parts water. Winter Driving Conditions: 1 part screen wash to 2 parts water. Severe Driving Conditions: Use undiluted.

ESSENTIAL CAR MAINTENANCE: Include Carpride All Seasons Screenwash as part of your regular car maintenance check list. Regularly check tyres, headlights, oil, windscreen wipers, screenwash, especially before long journeys
ABOUT THE PRODUCT: Carpride All Seasons Screenwash, 1L Bottle. Always store in an upright position, in a cool dry place.
